<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <img src="cid:logo" alt="Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;">
    </div>

  <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Hello {{oldTutorName}},</h2>

  <p>A tutoring session previously assigned to you has been <strong>reassigned to {{newTutorName}}</strong> by an administrator.</p>

  <h3>Session Details:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Course:</strong> {{courseName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Student:</strong> {{studentName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</li>
    <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</li>
    <li><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} hrs</li>
  </ul>

  <p>If you have any questions, please contact the admin.</p>

  <p>Thank you!</p>
</div>
